casebody.data:
Charles Russell RHINES, petitioner,
v.
Darin YOUNG, Warden. No. 18-8029. Supreme Court of the United States April 15, 2019.

Motion of Law Professors for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Motion of NAACP Legal Defense & Educational Fund, Inc. for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Motion of American Civil Liberties Union, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
